---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About Us | Surrey Contracting Limited"
  description="About Surrey Contracting Limited, a trusted contractor specialising in site enabling works, groundworks, bulk earthworks and commercial surfacing across Surrey, London and the South East for 15+ years."
  path="/about"
  active="about"
>

<!-- ============ PAGE HERO ============ -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="page-hero-img" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/bulk-earthworks.jpg')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-vignette"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container page-hero-inner">
    <nav class="crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      <span>About Us</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="page-title">About Surrey Contracting Limited</h1>
    <p class="page-lede">A trusted contractor specialising in demolition, groundworks, bulk earthworks and commercial surfacing solutions across Surrey, London and the South East.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ INTRO ============ -->
<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container page-grid">
    <aside class="page-side">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-yellow">Who we are</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Built on Experience.<br>Driven by Quality.</h2>
    </aside>
    <div class="page-prose">
      <p class="lede-dark">Surrey Contracting Limited is a trusted contractor specialising in site enabling works, groundworks, bulk earthworks and commercial surfacing solutions across Surrey, London and the South East.</p>
      <p>Built on over 15 years of industry experience, we provide turnkey external works solutions for commercial clients, developers, main contractors, local businesses and private homeowners, supporting both small and large-scale projects with professionalism, reliability and precision.</p>
      <p>Our team combines practical site experience with a strong commitment to quality workmanship, health and safety, and efficient project delivery. From initial site clearance and enabling works through to the groundworks phase and finishing works, we manage each stage with careful planning and attention to detail.</p>
      <p>We understand that every project, site and client requirement is different, which is why we take a tailored approach to every contract we undertake. Whether it's delivering a small works package, a large-scale commercial surfacing contract, or a full-scale groundworks project, our focus remains the same: delivering durable, high-quality results built to perform and stand the test of time.</p>
      <p>Using modern machinery, trusted materials and experienced contractors, Surrey Contracting Limited delivers projects efficiently while maintaining high standards across workmanship, communication, site safety and overall project delivery.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ WHAT WE DO ============ -->
<section class="page-section page-section-grey">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">What we do</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">A full-service contractor across Surrey.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="wwd-grid">
      <article class="wwd-card">
        <div class="wwd-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/groundworks.webp')"></div>
        <div class="wwd-body">
          <h3>Groundworks</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive groundwork solutions for small and large-scale projects, including site preparation, excavations, foundations, drainage, service trenches, sub-base preparation and associated infrastructure works.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="wwd-card">
        <div class="wwd-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/Demolition2.webp')"></div>
        <div class="wwd-body">
          <h3>Demolition </h3>
          <p>Practical site enabling works designed to prepare projects for the next stage of construction, including site clearance, soft strip works, asbestos removal, complete demolition, on-site concrete crushing, reduced level digs, access preparation, bulk excavation and early-stage external works.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="wwd-card">
        <div class="wwd-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/bulk-earthworks1.jpg')"></div>
        <div class="wwd-body">
          <h3>Bulk Earthworks</h3>
          <p>Large-scale excavation, site levelling, cut and fill works, land clearance, remediation support and earthmoving services completed using modern plant, machinery and our experienced operators.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="wwd-card">
        <div class="wwd-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/Commercial-Surfacing.png')"></div>
        <div class="wwd-body">
          <h3>Commercial Surfacing</h3>
          <p>Professional surfacing and finishing works for commercial premises, car parks, private roads, industrial estates, access routes, yards and external hardstanding areas, using high-quality materials and proven installation methods.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ OUR APPROACH ============ -->
<section class="page-section page-section-dark">
  <div class="container approach-grid">
    <div class="approach-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-yellow">Our approach</span>
      <h2 class="section-title light">Communication, reliability, attention to detail.</h2>
      <p>At Surrey Contracting Limited, we believe successful projects are built on clear communication, reliable delivery, health and safety, and attention to detail. We work closely with our clients, developers, homeowners, contractors and businesses to ensure each project is planned properly, managed efficiently and completed to a high standard.</p>
      <p>From initial site preparation and enabling works through to the groundworks phase and down to the finishing works, our approach is focused on providing a dependable turnkey service that supports both small and large-scale projects.</p>
      <p>Safety, efficiency, workmanship, communication and integrity remain at the core of everything we do, helping us build long-term relationships and a trusted reputation throughout Surrey, London and the South East of England.</p>
      <div class="approach-ctas">
        <a href="/#quote" class="btn btn-yellow">Request a quote</a>
        <a href="/#projects" class="btn btn-ghost-light">See our projects →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <ul class="approach-pillars">
      <li>
        <div class="pillar-num">01</div>
        <h4>Safety first</h4>
        <p>RAMS, toolbox talks and on-site supervision built into every job, not bolted on at the end.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="pillar-num">02</div>
        <h4>One team, one programme</h4>
        <p>Self-delivered disciplines mean fewer hand-offs, fewer surprises and a tighter critical path.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="pillar-num">03</div>
        <h4>Long-term relationships</h4>
        <p>Most of our work comes from repeat clients and referrals, the metric we care about most.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
</BaseLayout>
